# Intro

This is material for Psychology UGs at Lancaster Uni...

We will be using tidyverse:

```{r}
library(tidyverse)
```

You can do cool stuff like make graphs:

```{r}
mtcars %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = disp, y = mpg, colour = cyl)) +
  geom_point()
  
```
